section.title: The first 10000 FO words
section.p: The words should have been sorted after column 4, and thereafter after column 3. Instead, columd 4 are somewhat garbeled, but sorted in groups.

ol.li: first column = log(count(number of times in FO)/count(number of words in FO) x 100)
second column = log(count(number of times in Wikipedia)/count(number of words in Wikipedia) x 100)
fourth and fifth column: nob and sme
